"Installing>`_"

#: ../../content/administration/mobile.rst:55
msgid ""
"`Microsoft Support: Install, manage, or uninstall apps in Microsoft Edge "
"<https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/topic/install-manage-or-uninstall-apps-"
